text: Humayun Kabir Hiru is a Jatiya Samajtantrik Dal-JSD politician and the former Member of Parliament of Barguna-1. ==Career== Hiru was elected to parliament from Barguna-1 as a Jatiya Samajtantrik Dal-JSD candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Samajtantrik Dal-JSD politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Humayun Kabir Hiru
